<div class="jumbotron p-3 p-md-5 text-white rounded bg-dark">
  <div class="row justify-content-between">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h1 class="display-4">Joe Abbate</h1>
      <p class="lead my-3">Welcome! I'm Joe, currently a Information Security Engineer Intern at Citadel and RIT Cybersecurity BS 2024!</p>
