        <h3 class="mb-0">
          <a class="text-dark" href="/projects">My Projects</a>
        </h3>
        <p class="card-text mb-auto">I like to see what I can come up with on my free time. Some of it will work,
          others will be pure chaos. Regardless, I learn a lot from them and record them here!</p>
        <a href="/projects">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      <img class="card-img-right flex-auto d-none d-md-block" data-src="/assets/img/rusty.png" alt="Thumbnail [200x250]"
        src="/assets/img/rusty.png" data-holder-rendered="true" style="width: 200px; height: 250px;">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="card flex-md-row mb-4 box-shadow h-md-250">
      <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-start">
        <h3 class="mb-0">
          <a class="text-dark" href="https://csh.rit.edu/~skyz/AbbateResume.pdf" target="_blank">Resume</a>
        </h3>
        <p class="card-text mb-auto">Trying to learn about me all on one page? See here!</p>
        <a href="https://csh.rit.edu/~skyz/AbbateResume.pdf" target="_blank">View Resume</a>
      </div>
      <img class="card-img-right flex-auto d-none d-md-block" data-src="/assets/img/resume.png" alt="Thumbnail [200x250]"
        src="/assets/img/resume.png" data-holder-rendered="true" style="width: 200px; height: 250px;">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


